<doc id="67652" wikidata="Q2745892" url="?curid=67652" title="Demographics of Bahrain">
<text>The demographics of the population of Bahrain includes population density, ethnicity, education level, health of the populace, economic status, religious affiliations and other aspects of the population.

Most of the population of Bahrain is concentrated in the two principal cities, Manama and Al Muharraq.

== Population ==
=== Population census ===
